<HEADLINE> Basdaq Gains 3; Dow Adds 1  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- Stocks were modestly higher Monday, as wary
investors tried to reconcile positive economic news with fears of a
second-half earnings slowdown.
</P>
<P>
   In midday trading on Wall Street, the Dow Jones industrial
average was up 1.10 at 11,028.90.
</P>
<P>
   Broader stock indicators were higher.
</P>
<P>
   The Standard &AMP; Poor's 500 index was up 1.71 at 1,473.55, and the
Nasdaq composite index was up 2.64 at 3,792.11.
</P>
